bug.short_desc: [regression] could not auto close editor: Invalid thread access

long_desc.thetext:

Thanks for the bug report. This highlights two problems:
* Saving editor mementos modifies the workbench state. * Context persistence maybe invoked from non-UI threads.
I have added a flag to support saving the workbench state suppressing any modifications and added checks that calls are on the UI thread.
